  "text": "Seven 1-week-old seedlings were ground in 200 mL of 90% acetone. Chlorophyll extracts were recovered from the supernatant after centrifugation at 13,000 rpm for 5 min. Absorbances at 645 and 663 nm were measured using a photospectrometer (GENESYS 5; Spectronic Unicam). Chlorophyll content was determined using the formula 20.2(A645) + 8.02(A663) [CITATION_1] .",
